data.description: The Onyx by Windmill Homes - This beautiful townhome boasts a bright open floor plan with high-end finishes throughout including quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom tiled backsplash, laminate wood floors, and private balcony off primary bedroom which is accentuated with an en suite that includes a fully tiled walk-in shower. Laundry located on upper level. The Onyx has 2 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms along with oversized 2- car attached garage and a 678 sq ft unfinished basement and so much more including all kitchen appliances and window coverings! Brookstone offers maintenance free living so you can enjoy your down time!
